01:48:02,601 --> 01:48:05,520
A fucking lineup, that's what for.

1834
01:48:05,688 --> 01:48:07,063
They got a witness, evidently.

1835
01:48:07,273 --> 01:48:09,899
Now, look, I found you a guy,
his name is Gar Girard.

1836
01:48:10,067 --> 01:48:12,735
He's a top-flight criminal lawyer.
He's tough, hard-nosed.

1837
01:48:12,903 --> 01:48:15,655
Don't you talk to anybody else.
Just get there.

1838
01:48:16,407 --> 01:48:20,076
- I'll be there.
- Griffin, this is a tough one.

1839
01:48:20,286 --> 01:48:21,619
Good luck.

1840
01:48:21,787 --> 01:48:22,996
