- Can you guarantee that ending?

2005
01:59:42,467 --> 01:59:45,928
- If the price is right, you got it.
- If you can guarantee me that ending...

2006
01:59:46,096 --> 01:59:48,472
...you got a deal.
- I guarantee it, Griff.

2007
01:59:48,682 --> 01:59:51,976
- What do you call this thing anyway?
- The Player.

2008
01:59:52,185 --> 01:59:53,811
GRIFFIN:
The Player.

2009
01:59:57,065 --> 01:59:58,107
I like that.

2010
02:00:01,486 --> 02:00:03,529
What took you so long?

2011
02:00:03,738 --> 02:00:06,198
Traffic was a bitch.

